IN the Name of God, Amen. I A. B. of &c. being in good health of Body, and of sound and perfect Mind and Memory, Praise be therefore given to Almighty God, do make and ordain this my present Last Will and Testament, in manner and form following (that is to say); First and principally, I commend my Soul into the Hands of Almighty God, hoping through the Merits, Death, and Passion, 
   •
f my Saviour Iesus Christ, to have full and free Pardon and Forgiveness of all my Sins, and to inherit everlasting Life; and my Body I commit to the Earth, to be decently buried at the discretion of my Executor hereafter named; And as touching the disposition of all such Temporall Estate, as it hath pleased Almighty God to bestow upon me, I give and dispose thereof, as followeth;
